Cool, beautiful.

549
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:48,601
- I'd like very, very beautiful flowers.
- Yeah.

550
00:28:48,685 --> 00:28:50,311
You need a big bouquet?

551
00:28:50,395 --> 00:28:52,564
- Hmm, yeah.
- For present?

552
00:28:52,647 --> 00:28:54,524
- For present.
- Okay.

553
00:29:19,007 --> 00:29:19,841
Dear Maho,

554
00:29:19,924 --> 00:29:21,843
I want to thank you for the other day.

555
00:29:21,926 --> 00:29:25,597
I will be waiting for you at 7:00 p.m.
today (Day Eight) in front of Margaux.

556
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:27,474
Don't worry if you have other plans!

557
00:29:27,557 --> 00:29:28,391
From Aru

