00:57:53,511 --> 00:57:56,264
I heard you're going out

1043
00:57:58,057 --> 00:57:59,642
with Tohko tomorrow.

1044
00:58:00,226 --> 00:58:01,060
I…

1045
00:58:02,312 --> 00:58:03,563
I canceled that.

1046
00:58:04,647 --> 00:58:05,482
What?

1047
00:58:06,357 --> 00:58:09,152
I really want to go

1048
00:58:09,986 --> 00:58:13,615
on a date with you one last time.

1049
00:58:14,908 --> 00:58:16,201
And I want to

1050
00:58:17,660 --> 00:58:23,625
tell you my honest feelings.

1051
00:58:27,295 --> 00:58:28,129
Hmm.

1052
00:58:29,756 --> 00:58:32,425
I have plans

1053
00:58:33,384 --> 00:58:36,804
to go on a date with Kensuke tomorrow.

1054
00:58:38,765 --> 00:58:42,310
Can I see you just for a little bit?

1055
00:58:45,146 --> 00:58:47,065
Can I have some time to think?

1056
00:58:47,148 --> 00:58:48,483
Yes. No problem.

1057
00:58:49,108 --> 00:58:50,235
Of course.

1058
00:58:50,860 --> 00:58:52,320
- Excuse me.
- Okay.

1059
00:58:59,744 --> 00:59:00,662
What should I do?

1060
00:59:13,299 --> 00:59:16,177
I wanted to see him tomorrow.

1061
00:59:16,678 --> 00:59:18,930
Yeah, let it all out tonight.

1062
00:59:19,931 --> 00:59:20,848
Let's cry.

1063
00:59:21,516 --> 00:59:23,851
- Good luck tomorrow.
- Yeah, tomorrow.

1064
00:59:23,935 --> 00:59:25,728
- We'll see.
- Are you excited?

1065
00:59:25,812 --> 00:59:27,355
- Anxious?
- Nervous.

1066
00:59:27,438 --> 00:59:28,606
- Nervous?
- Yeah.

1067
00:59:28,690 --> 00:59:30,191
- In a good way?
- In a good way.

1068
00:59:30,275 --> 00:59:31,818
- That's nice.
- Right?

1069
00:59:31,901 --> 00:59:33,653
It was worth coming on this trip.

1070
00:59:33,736 --> 00:59:35,071
- Right?
- Yeah.

1071
00:59:36,739 --> 00:59:38,241
Just now,

1072
00:59:38,324 --> 00:59:42,620
a lady gave me a flower during dinner.

1073
00:59:43,288 --> 00:59:44,289
I'll give it to you.

1074
00:59:44,789 --> 00:59:46,040
- Really?
- Yeah.

1075
00:59:47,000 --> 00:59:48,585
- Are you sure?
- Good luck tomorrow.

1076
00:59:48,668 --> 00:59:50,587
- Thank you.
- Rest well.

1077
00:59:52,338 --> 00:59:53,673
- Thanks.
- Good night.

1078
00:59:53,756 --> 00:59:54,757
Take care.

1079
00:59:55,717 --> 00:59:57,385
He does so well when he's drunk.

1080
00:59:58,136 --> 01:00:00,805
He's useless until he has some alcohol.

1081
01:00:01,306 --> 01:00:03,516
- He's best when drunk.
- It's like drunken boxing.

1082
01:00:05,184 --> 01:00:08,104
- I want to see her on the last day.
- Right.

1083
01:00:08,187 --> 01:00:12,025
- They might not choose us.
- Yeah.

1084
01:00:12,108 --> 01:00:13,401
Yudai too.

1085
01:00:13,484 --> 01:00:15,069
- Was it yesterday?
- Yeah.

1086
01:00:15,153 --> 01:00:16,946
He handed his Wish Letter

1087
01:00:17,864 --> 01:00:18,823
to Nanami.

1088
01:00:18,906 --> 01:00:19,866
But yesterday,

1089
01:00:19,949 --> 01:00:22,452
he went to Grasse.

1090
01:00:22,535 --> 01:00:25,496
- Right. Maho asked him out.
- Yeah.

1091
01:00:25,580 --> 01:00:29,083
I think Yudai is really torn as well.

1092
01:00:45,350 --> 01:00:46,726
I promised Kensuke

1093
01:00:47,977 --> 01:00:52,190
that we will go on a date tomorrow.

1094
01:00:53,024 --> 01:00:55,652
I want to go on that date.

1095
01:01:00,907 --> 01:01:02,950
In that case, if I happen to

1096
01:01:05,078 --> 01:01:06,537
see you in the city,

1097
01:01:07,038 --> 01:01:11,000
would it be possible
to have a little bit of time to talk?

1098
01:01:12,377 --> 01:01:13,670
Is that okay?

1099
01:01:14,587 --> 01:01:15,421
Yes.

1100
01:01:17,423 --> 01:01:19,050
Okay. Thank you.

1101
01:01:19,550 --> 01:01:21,386
Sorry I took so long.

1102
01:01:21,469 --> 01:01:25,139
- No, I apologize. You must be tired.
- That's okay.

1103
01:01:25,223 --> 01:01:26,933
If he meets her in the city?

1104
01:01:27,016 --> 01:01:29,477
- Is he going to test his fate?
- I see.

1105
01:01:30,144 --> 01:01:32,188
- Good night.
- Good night.

1106
01:02:20,528 --> 01:02:21,362
Dear Yudai,

1107
01:02:21,446 --> 01:02:23,281
Thank you for today. I had fun!

1108
01:02:23,364 --> 01:02:27,702
If you are free tomorrow (Day Nine),
will you go for lunch with me?

1109
01:02:27,785 --> 01:02:31,372
I will be waiting for you
at 12:00 p.m. at Place Masséna.

1110
01:02:31,456 --> 01:02:32,457
From Maho

